lead_paragraph: New Zealand batsmen have the necessary skills to negotiate the Indian spinners on turning tracks but must apply themselves for longer periods, captain Kane Williamson said after his team's loss in the opening test on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Williamson Wants More Application From New Zealand Batsmen
